properties.name: allowExporting
properties.description: Specifies whether data from this column should be exported. Applies only if the column is [visible].

properties.name: allowFiltering
properties.description: Specifies whether data can be filtered by this column.

properties.name: allowGrouping
properties.description: Specifies whether the user can group data by values of this column. Applies only when grouping is enabled.

properties.name: autoExpandGroup
properties.description: Specifies whether groups appear expanded or not when records are grouped by a specific column. Setting this property makes sense only when grouping is [allowed] for this column.

properties.name: buttons
properties.description: Allows you to customize buttons in the edit column or create a custom [command column]. Applies only if the column's [type] is *"buttons"*.

properties.name: calculateGroupValue
properties.description: Sets custom column values used to group grid records.

properties.name: cellComponent
properties.description: An alias for the [cellTemplate] property specified in React. Accepts a custom component. Refer to [Using a Custom Component] for more information.

properties.name: cellRender
properties.description: An alias for the [cellTemplate] property specified in React. Accepts a rendering function. Refer to [Using a Rendering Function] for more information.

properties.name: cellTemplate
properties.description: Specifies a custom template for data cells.

properties.name: columns
properties.description: An array of grid columns.

properties.name: editCellComponent
properties.description: An alias for the [editCellTemplate] property specified in React. Accepts a custom component. Refer to [Using a Custom Component] for more information.

properties.name: editCellRender
properties.description: An alias for the [editCellTemplate] property specified in React. Accepts a rendering function. Refer to [Using a Rendering Function] for more information.

properties.name: editCellTemplate
properties.description: Specifies a custom template for data cells in an editing state.

properties.name: groupCellComponent
properties.description: An alias for the [groupCellTemplate] property specified in React. Accepts a custom component. Refer to [Using a Custom Component] for more information.

properties.name: groupCellRender
properties.description: An alias for the [groupCellTemplate] property specified in React. Accepts a rendering function. Refer to [Using a Rendering Function] for more information.

properties.name: groupCellTemplate
properties.description: Specifies a custom template for group cells (group rows).

properties.name: groupIndex
properties.description: Specifies the index of a column when grid records are [grouped] by the values of this column.

properties.name: headerCellComponent
properties.description: An alias for the [headerCellTemplate] property specified in React. Accepts a custom component. Refer to [Using a Custom Component] for more information.

properties.name: headerCellRender
properties.description: An alias for the [headerCellTemplate] property specified in React. Accepts a rendering function. Refer to [Using a Rendering Function] for more information.

properties.name: headerCellTemplate
properties.description: Specifies a custom template for column headers.

properties.name: showWhenGrouped
properties.description: Specifies whether or not to display the column when grid records are grouped by it.

properties.name: type
properties.description: Specifies the [command column] that this object customizes.
